                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2006" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0268</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8530 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中信集团探索资产证券化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The way of CITIC Group Asset Securitization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陆剑清</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中信集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">49 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资产证券化；路径选择；优化设计；中信集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Asset securitization; Path selection; Optimized design; CITIC Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了在2013年中国经济动荡不安的大背景下，同时在金融市场遭受了“钱荒”的袭击之后，国务院在2013年7月，为稳定市场预期，缓解市场流动性问题，就此发布了《关于金融支持经济结构调整和转型升级的指导意见》，其中明确地提出了“逐步推进资产证券化常态化发展”的要求。中信集团作为国有独资公司、大型综合类央企，应当积极推动国家战略的实施，在满足国家利益的前提下，利用资产证券化推进国家经济转型发展并同时促进集团的进一步扩张，逐步实现“盘活存量，盘活经济”的整体目标。从国外的发展经验来看，资产证券化在过去化解经济危机的过程当中起到了举足轻重的作用，而且其主导方都是国家政府及其相关机构，效果非常明显。而中信集团作为国有独资公司这一特殊的经济运行主体，恰好可以担当推动这一战略实施的主要机构。资产证券化的发展对于我国经济的转型以及集团的发展都具有极其重要的意义，但首先要找准切入点，同时设计好发展的路径，这样才能收获理想的效果。文中给出了《中信集团推动资产证券化在我国发展的路径选择及优化设计》，详细地表达了作者的想法和观点，以供大家参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After the case described in the 2013 Chinese economic turmoil in the background, while in the financial markets suffered a &quot;money shortage&quot; attacks , the State Council in July 2013 , to stabilize the market expected, easing market liquidity issues for this release the &quot;Guidance on financial support for economic structure adjustment and transformation and upgrading ,&quot; which explicitly proposed a &quot; gradual normalization of promoting the development of asset securitization &quot; requirement . CITIC Group , a state-owned company , large integrated central enterprises should actively promote the implementation of national strategies , to meet the national interests of the premise, the use of asset securitization to promote the country&#39;s economic transformation and development and also promote the further expansion of the Group , the progressive realization &quot; revitalize stock , revitalize the economy , &quot;the overall goal. From the perspective of the development experience of foreign countries , asset securitization in the past the process of resolving the economic crisis has played a pivotal role , and its leading party is the national government and its related agencies , the effect is very obvious. The state-owned company , CITIC Group, as the economic operation of this special body , just to play a major agencies to promote the implementation of this strategy . Development of asset securitization have for China&#39;s economic transformation and development of the Group&#39;s extremely important , but we must first identify the entry point , while good design path of development , so as to gain the desired results. This paper presents the &quot; path of CITIC Group to promote the development of asset securitization selection and optimization of the design ,&quot; details the author&#39;s express thoughts and ideas , for your reference .
Key words: 
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融资产管理》、《证券投资分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资产证券化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-09</td>
